	     <form action=/cgi-bin/mrate.pl name=f103605316493487>
	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=>RE: What Race is best for SK?!?</a> <a id=fs8 href=#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Thu, Oct 31st 3:32 AM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=125915><span id= >Kairos</span></a><br><span id=notbold>4 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>The Gnome does NOT level the fastest of all the Shadow Knight races. Here's how exp works for the races SKs can be:<br><br>(100 is the median, and only the Halfling gets a bonus, at 95)<br><br>100 - Human<br>100 - Dark Elf<br>100 - Gnome<br>100 - Erudite<br>115 - Ogre<br>120 - Troll<br>120 - Iksar<br><br>This number is used as a multiplier interally by the game to determine the amount of exp you need to get a level. This means that Ogres, Trolls, and Iksars level more slowly. At low levels, this is fairly painless, but it gets considerably worse after about level 50, so I've heard.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Oct 31 03:37:52 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
